{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"URLSearchParams","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL_API\">URL API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/append\"><code>append()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/delete\"><code>delete()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries\"><code>entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/forEach\"><code>forEach()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/has\"><code>has()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/keys\"><code>keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/set\"><code>set()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/sort\"><code>sort()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a URL API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>A interface <strong><code>URLSearchParams</code></strong> define métodos de utilização para trabalhar com query string de uma URL.</p>\n\n<p>Uma implementação do objeto <code>URLSearchParams</code> pode diretamente ser usado em uma estrutura <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/for...of\"><code>for...of</code></a>, em vez de <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries\"><code>entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>: <code>for (var p of mySearchParams)</code> é equivalente de <code>for (var p of mySearchParams.entries())</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"construtor","title":"Construtor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Construtor retorna um objeto <code>URLSearchParams</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Esta interface não herda nenhuma propriedade.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Esta interface não herda nenhum método.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.append_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/append\"><code>URLSearchParams.append()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Acrescenta um par de chave/valor específica com um novo parâmetro de busca.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.delete_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/delete\"><code>URLSearchParams.delete()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Exclui o parâmetro de busca informado, e seu valor associado, da lista de parâmetros de busca.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.entries_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries\"><code>URLSearchParams.entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a> permitindo obter por todos os pares de chave/valor contidos neste objeto.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.get\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get\"><code>URLSearchParams.get()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna o primeiro valor associado ao parâmetro de busca informado.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.getall_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/getAll\"><code>URLSearchParams.getAll()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna todos os valores associados com o parâmetro de busca encontrado.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.has_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/has\"><code>URLSearchParams.has()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> indicando se cada um dos parâmetros de busca existe.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.keys_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/keys\"><code>URLSearchParams.keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a> permitindo obter todas as chaves dos pares de chave/valor contido neste objeto.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.set_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/set\"><code>URLSearchParams.set()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Define o valor associado ao parâmetro de busca com o valor informado. Se tiver mutios valores, exclua os outros.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.tostring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/toString\"><code>URLSearchParams.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna uma string contendo uma query string adequada pra usar numa URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlsearchparams.values\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/values\"><code>URLSearchParams.values()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a> permitindo obter todos os valores dos pares de chave/valor contido neste objeto.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> stringParams <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"q=URLUtils.searchParams&amp;topic=api\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> paramsBusca <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URLSearchParams</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>stringParams<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Iterar os parâmetros de busca.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> p <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> paramsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"topic\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"topic\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"api\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"topic\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// [\"api\"]</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"topic\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"webdev\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"q=URLUtils.searchParams&amp;topic=api&amp;topic=webdev\"</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"topic\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"More webdev\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"q=URLUtils.searchParams&amp;topic=More+webdev\"</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">delete</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"topic\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nparamsBusca<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"q=URLUtils.searchParams\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Situação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#urlsearchparams\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">URL<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'URLSearchParams' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>49</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/29\" title=\"Released on 2014-04-29.\">29.0</a> (29.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>36</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>entries()</code>, <code>keys()</code>, <code>values()</code>, e suporte de <code>for...of</code></td>\n   <td>49</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/44\" title=\"Released on 2016-01-26.\">44.0</a> (44.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>36</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>49</td>\n   <td>29.0 (29.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>49</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>entries()</code>, <code>keys()</code>, <code>values()</code>, e suporte de <code>for...of</code></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>49</td>\n   <td>44.0 (44.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>49</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Outras interfaces relacionadas com URL: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils</code></a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/updates/2016/01/urlsearchparams?hl=en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Google Developers: Easy URL manipulation with URLSearchParams</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<dl>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Construtor","id":"construtor"},{"text":"Propriedades","id":"propriedades"},{"text":"Métodos","id":"métodos"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A interface URLSearchParams define métodos de utilização para trabalhar com query string de uma URL.","popularity":0.0011,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"URLSearchParams","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"URLSearchParams","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"URLSearchParams","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"URLSearchParams","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"URLSearchParams","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"URLSearchParams","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"URLSearchParams","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"URLSearchParams","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/urlsearchparams","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/urlsearchparams/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams","title":"URLSearchParams"}],"pageTitle":"URLSearchParams - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}